{"data":{"content":{"edges":[{"node":{"id":"2ae0e8fc-740f-5aef-8b06-87564bfde23d","html":"<p>如果你用過 Font Awesome 等圖標，你可能會覺得它們很好看，用起來很很方便。但是，在用戶點擊這些圖標的時候，它們是不會有反應的。如果有這些圖標會動的話，那就更加好。Titanic 提供一系列的動畫圖標，以及以 JavaScript 的調用圖標動畫的方法。</p>\n<p>如果你想要看 Hello, World 的版本的話，你可以到我的 <a href=\"https://codepen.io/calpa/pen/xrzPxx\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"nofollow noopener noreferrer\">Codepen</a> 裡面，測試一下。</p>\n<p><img src=\"https://i.imgur.com/bLmxAZ3.gif\" alt=\"Preview\"></p>\n<h2 id=\"安裝方法\"><a href=\"#%E5%AE%89%E8%A3%9D%E6%96%B9%E6%B3%95\" aria-label=\"安裝方法 permalink\" class=\"anchor\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" focusable=\"false\" height=\"16\" version=\"1.1\" viewBox=\"0 0 16 16\" width=\"16\"><path fill-rule=\"evenodd\" d=\"M4 9h1v1H4c-1.5 0-3-1.69-3-3.5S2.55 3 4 3h4c1.45 0 3 1.69 3 3.5 0 1.41-.91 2.72-2 3.25V8.59c.58-.45 1-1.27 1-2.09C10 5.22 8.98 4 8 4H4c-.98 0-2 1.22-2 2.5S3 9 4 9zm9-3h-1v1h1c1 0 2 1.22 2 2.5S13.98 12 13 12H9c-.98 0-2-1.22-2-2.5 0-.83.42-1.64 1-2.09V6.25c-1.09.53-2 1.84-2 3.25C6 11.31 7.55 13 9 13h4c1.45 0 3-1.69 3-3.5S14.5 6 13 6z\"></path></svg></a>安裝方法</h2>\n<p>你可以使用 CDN 或者 npm 來安裝 Titanic。</p>\n<h3 id=\"cdn\"><a href=\"#cdn\" aria-label=\"cdn permalink\" class=\"anchor\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" focusable=\"false\" height=\"16\" version=\"1.1\" viewBox=\"0 0 16 16\" width=\"16\"><path fill-rule=\"evenodd\" d=\"M4 9h1v1H4c-1.5 0-3-1.69-3-3.5S2.55 3 4 3h4c1.45 0 3 1.69 3 3.5 0 1.41-.91 2.72-2 3.25V8.59c.58-.45 1-1.27 1-2.09C10 5.22 8.98 4 8 4H4c-.98 0-2 1.22-2 2.5S3 9 4 9zm9-3h-1v1h1c1 0 2 1.22 2 2.5S13.98 12 13 12H9c-.98 0-2-1.22-2-2.5 0-.83.42-1.64 1-2.09V6.25c-1.09.53-2 1.84-2 3.25C6 11.31 7.55 13 9 13h4c1.45 0 3-1.69 3-3.5S14.5 6 13 6z\"></path></svg></a>CDN</h3>\n<p>直接在 HTML head 裡面加進下面的字符。</p>\n<div class=\"gatsby-highlight\" data-language=\"text\"><pre style=\"counter-reset: linenumber NaN\" class=\"language-text line-numbers\"><code class=\"language-text\">&lt;script src=&quot;https://cdn.rawgit.com/icons8/titanic/master/dist/js/titanic.min.js&quot;&gt;&lt;/script&gt;\n&lt;script src=&quot;https://cdnjs.cloudflare.com/ajax/libs/bodymovin/4.5.9/bodymovin.min.js&quot;&gt;&lt;/script&gt;</code><span aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"line-numbers-rows\" style=\"white-space: normal; width: auto; left: 0;\"><span></span><span></span></span></pre></div>\n<p>然後在 body 的部分初始化 Titanic。</p>\n<div class=\"gatsby-highlight\" data-language=\"text\"><pre style=\"counter-reset: linenumber NaN\" class=\"language-text line-numbers\"><code class=\"language-text\">&lt;script&gt;\n    var titanic = new Titanic();\n&lt;/script&gt;</code><span aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"line-numbers-rows\" style=\"white-space: normal; width: auto; left: 0;\"><span></span><span></span><span></span></span></pre></div>\n<p>你可以透過這種標籤來加上 Titanic 圖標。</p>\n<div class=\"gatsby-highlight\" data-language=\"text\"><pre style=\"counter-reset: linenumber NaN\" class=\"language-text line-numbers\"><code class=\"language-text\">&lt;div class=&#39;titanic titanic_chat&#39;&gt;&lt;/div&gt;</code><span aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"line-numbers-rows\" style=\"white-space: normal; width: auto; left: 0;\"><span></span></span></pre></div>\n<p><img src=\"https://i.imgur.com/aiG4BYo.png\" alt=\"All icons\"></p>\n<p>你可以透過<a href=\"https://rawgit.com/icons8/titanic/master/demo/index.html\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"nofollow noopener noreferrer\">這裡</a>查找 Titanic 所支持的圖標，把 chat 換成以下的字詞：</p>\n<ul>\n<li>caps</li>\n<li>chat</li>\n<li>checkbox</li>\n<li>expand</li>\n<li>cheap</li>\n<li>expensive</li>\n<li>idea</li>\n<li>mailbox</li>\n<li>mic</li>\n<li>no-mic</li>\n<li>online</li>\n<li>pause</li>\n<li>power</li>\n<li>shopping</li>\n<li>smile</li>\n<li>stop</li>\n<li>unlock</li>\n<li>zoom</li>\n</ul>\n<h3 id=\"npm\"><a href=\"#npm\" aria-label=\"npm permalink\" class=\"anchor\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" focusable=\"false\" height=\"16\" version=\"1.1\" viewBox=\"0 0 16 16\" width=\"16\"><path fill-rule=\"evenodd\" d=\"M4 9h1v1H4c-1.5 0-3-1.69-3-3.5S2.55 3 4 3h4c1.45 0 3 1.69 3 3.5 0 1.41-.91 2.72-2 3.25V8.59c.58-.45 1-1.27 1-2.09C10 5.22 8.98 4 8 4H4c-.98 0-2 1.22-2 2.5S3 9 4 9zm9-3h-1v1h1c1 0 2 1.22 2 2.5S13.98 12 13 12H9c-.98 0-2-1.22-2-2.5 0-.83.42-1.64 1-2.09V6.25c-1.09.53-2 1.84-2 3.25C6 11.31 7.55 13 9 13h4c1.45 0 3-1.69 3-3.5S14.5 6 13 6z\"></path></svg></a>npm</h3>\n<div class=\"gatsby-highlight\" data-language=\"text\"><pre style=\"counter-reset: linenumber NaN\" class=\"language-text line-numbers\"><code class=\"language-text\">npm install titanic-icons --save</code><span aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"line-numbers-rows\" style=\"white-space: normal; width: auto; left: 0;\"><span></span></span></pre></div>\n<p>鏈接：<a href=\"https://www.npmjs.com/package/titanic-icons\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"nofollow noopener noreferrer\">titanic-icons - npmjs</a></p>\n<h3 id=\"使用你自己的備份\"><a href=\"#%E4%BD%BF%E7%94%A8%E4%BD%A0%E8%87%AA%E5%B7%B1%E7%9A%84%E5%82%99%E4%BB%BD\" aria-label=\"使用你自己的備份 permalink\" class=\"anchor\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" focusable=\"false\" height=\"16\" version=\"1.1\" viewBox=\"0 0 16 16\" width=\"16\"><path fill-rule=\"evenodd\" d=\"M4 9h1v1H4c-1.5 0-3-1.69-3-3.5S2.55 3 4 3h4c1.45 0 3 1.69 3 3.5 0 1.41-.91 2.72-2 3.25V8.59c.58-.45 1-1.27 1-2.09C10 5.22 8.98 4 8 4H4c-.98 0-2 1.22-2 2.5S3 9 4 9zm9-3h-1v1h1c1 0 2 1.22 2 2.5S13.98 12 13 12H9c-.98 0-2-1.22-2-2.5 0-.83.42-1.64 1-2.09V6.25c-1.09.53-2 1.84-2 3.25C6 11.31 7.55 13 9 13h4c1.45 0 3-1.69 3-3.5S14.5 6 13 6z\"></path></svg></a>使用你自己的備份</h3>\n<p>如果你喜歡在自己的伺服器，而不是 rawgit 去使用 Titanic 的話，你只需要把 base URL 傳進 init() 裡面。</p>\n<div class=\"gatsby-highlight\" data-language=\"javascript\"><pre style=\"counter-reset: linenumber NaN\" class=\"language-javascript line-numbers\"><code class=\"language-javascript\">titanic<span class=\"token punctuation\">.</span><span class=\"token function\">begin</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">(</span><span class=\"token string\">\"/my/base/directory/\"</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">)</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">;</span></code><span aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"line-numbers-rows\" style=\"white-space: normal; width: auto; left: 0;\"><span></span></span></pre></div>\n<p>然後，當你有一個 div，id=\"chat\" 的時候，Titanic 會自動檢測所有在 /my/base/directory/chat.json 裡面的圖標。</p>\n<h2 id=\"api\"><a href=\"#api\" aria-label=\"api permalink\" class=\"anchor\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" focusable=\"false\" height=\"16\" version=\"1.1\" viewBox=\"0 0 16 16\" width=\"16\"><path fill-rule=\"evenodd\" d=\"M4 9h1v1H4c-1.5 0-3-1.69-3-3.5S2.55 3 4 3h4c1.45 0 3 1.69 3 3.5 0 1.41-.91 2.72-2 3.25V8.59c.58-.45 1-1.27 1-2.09C10 5.22 8.98 4 8 4H4c-.98 0-2 1.22-2 2.5S3 9 4 9zm9-3h-1v1h1c1 0 2 1.22 2 2.5S13.98 12 13 12H9c-.98 0-2-1.22-2-2.5 0-.83.42-1.64 1-2.09V6.25c-1.09.53-2 1.84-2 3.25C6 11.31 7.55 13 9 13h4c1.45 0 3-1.69 3-3.5S14.5 6 13 6z\"></path></svg></a>API</h2>\n<ul>\n<li><code class=\"language-text\">titanic.isInitialized()</code> -- 返回 true / false</li>\n<li><code class=\"language-text\">titanic.items</code> -- 返回包含所有 titanic 圖標的一個 Array</li>\n<li><code class=\"language-text\">titanic.items[index].on(), titanic.items[index].off(), titanic.items[index].play()</code> -- 調整動畫 by index</li>\n<li><code class=\"language-text\">titanic.on(token), titanic.off(token), titanic.play(token)</code> -- 調整動畫 by token (name)</li>\n</ul>\n<h2 id=\"例子\"><a href=\"#%E4%BE%8B%E5%AD%90\" aria-label=\"例子 permalink\" class=\"anchor\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" focusable=\"false\" height=\"16\" version=\"1.1\" viewBox=\"0 0 16 16\" width=\"16\"><path fill-rule=\"evenodd\" d=\"M4 9h1v1H4c-1.5 0-3-1.69-3-3.5S2.55 3 4 3h4c1.45 0 3 1.69 3 3.5 0 1.41-.91 2.72-2 3.25V8.59c.58-.45 1-1.27 1-2.09C10 5.22 8.98 4 8 4H4c-.98 0-2 1.22-2 2.5S3 9 4 9zm9-3h-1v1h1c1 0 2 1.22 2 2.5S13.98 12 13 12H9c-.98 0-2-1.22-2-2.5 0-.83.42-1.64 1-2.09V6.25c-1.09.53-2 1.84-2 3.25C6 11.31 7.55 13 9 13h4c1.45 0 3-1.69 3-3.5S14.5 6 13 6z\"></path></svg></a>例子</h2>\n<div class=\"gatsby-highlight\" data-language=\"text\"><pre style=\"counter-reset: linenumber NaN\" class=\"language-text line-numbers\"><code class=\"language-text\">&lt;head&gt;\n    &lt;!--Inserting the scripts once for the whole page--&gt;\n    &lt;script src=&quot;https://cdn.rawgit.com/icons8/titanic/master/dist/js/titanic.min.js&quot;&gt;&lt;/script&gt;\n    &lt;script src=&quot;https://cdnjs.cloudflare.com/ajax/libs/bodymovin/4.5.9/bodymovin.min.js&quot;&gt;&lt;/script&gt;\n&lt;/head&gt;\n&lt;body&gt;\n    &lt;!--Inserting an icon--&gt;\n    &lt;div class=&#39;titanic titanic-checkbox&#39;&gt;&lt;/div&gt;\n\n    &lt;!--Initializing--&gt;\n    &lt;script&gt;\n      // 避免找不到 Titanic 。。。\n      if (window.Titanic) {\n        var titanic = new Titanic({\n          hover: true, // auto animated on hover (default true)\n          click: true  // auto animated on click/tap (default false)\n        });\n      }\n    &lt;/script&gt;\n\n    &lt;!--Clicking turns this icon on--&gt;\n    &lt;button onclick=&quot;titanic.on(getElementById(&#39;checkbox&#39;).value)&quot;&gt;On&lt;/button&gt;\n&lt;/body&gt;</code><span aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"line-numbers-rows\" style=\"white-space: normal; width: auto; left: 0;\"><span></span><span></span><span></span><span></span><span></span><span></span><span></span><span></span><span></span><span></span><span></span><span></span><span></span><span></span><span></span><span></span><span></span><span></span><span></span><span></span><span></span><span></span><span></span></span></pre></div>\n<h2 id=\"原作者的話\"><a href=\"#%E5%8E%9F%E4%BD%9C%E8%80%85%E7%9A%84%E8%A9%B1\" aria-label=\"原作者的話 permalink\" class=\"anchor\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" focusable=\"false\" height=\"16\" version=\"1.1\" viewBox=\"0 0 16 16\" width=\"16\"><path fill-rule=\"evenodd\" d=\"M4 9h1v1H4c-1.5 0-3-1.69-3-3.5S2.55 3 4 3h4c1.45 0 3 1.69 3 3.5 0 1.41-.91 2.72-2 3.25V8.59c.58-.45 1-1.27 1-2.09C10 5.22 8.98 4 8 4H4c-.98 0-2 1.22-2 2.5S3 9 4 9zm9-3h-1v1h1c1 0 2 1.22 2 2.5S13.98 12 13 12H9c-.98 0-2-1.22-2-2.5 0-.83.42-1.64 1-2.09V6.25c-1.09.53-2 1.84-2 3.25C6 11.31 7.55 13 9 13h4c1.45 0 3-1.69 3-3.5S14.5 6 13 6z\"></path></svg></a>原作者的話</h2>\n<blockquote>\n<p>JavaScript is basically <a href=\"https://github.com/bodymovin/bodymovin\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"nofollow noopener noreferrer\">bodymovin</a> plus few lines of my code. It's a solid library with an awesome name. Thank you, guys.</p>\n</blockquote>\n<blockquote>\n<p>Icons are created by <a href=\"https://dribbble.com/imargarita\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"nofollow noopener noreferrer\">Margarita Ivanchikova</a> from <a href=\"https://icons8.com/\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"nofollow noopener noreferrer\">Icons8</a>. She has many more awesome animations in her portfolio.</p>\n</blockquote>\n<blockquote>\n<p>The code rewritten by <a href=\"https://github.com/dhilt\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"nofollow noopener noreferrer\">Denis Alexanov</a>, my teacher and guru. Thank you!</p>\n</blockquote>\n<blockquote>\n<p>Project is produced by Icons8, author of the famous icon library, <a href=\"https://iconpharm.com\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"nofollow noopener noreferrer\">IconPharm</a>, and <a href=\"https://sleeklogos.design\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"nofollow noopener noreferrer\">Sleek Logos</a>.</p>\n</blockquote>\n<blockquote>\n<p>The code is created by Icons8</p>\n</blockquote>\n<p><img src=\"https://i.imgur.com/p8Xoj9l.gif\" alt=\"Magritte\"></p>\n<p>Github Repo: <a href=\"https://github.com/icons8/titanic\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"nofollow noopener noreferrer\">icons 8 / titanic</a></p>\n<h2 id=\"感想\"><a href=\"#%E6%84%9F%E6%83%B3\" aria-label=\"感想 permalink\" class=\"anchor\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" focusable=\"false\" height=\"16\" version=\"1.1\" viewBox=\"0 0 16 16\" width=\"16\"><path fill-rule=\"evenodd\" d=\"M4 9h1v1H4c-1.5 0-3-1.69-3-3.5S2.55 3 4 3h4c1.45 0 3 1.69 3 3.5 0 1.41-.91 2.72-2 3.25V8.59c.58-.45 1-1.27 1-2.09C10 5.22 8.98 4 8 4H4c-.98 0-2 1.22-2 2.5S3 9 4 9zm9-3h-1v1h1c1 0 2 1.22 2 2.5S13.98 12 13 12H9c-.98 0-2-1.22-2-2.5 0-.83.42-1.64 1-2.09V6.25c-1.09.53-2 1.84-2 3.25C6 11.31 7.55 13 9 13h4c1.45 0 3-1.69 3-3.5S14.5 6 13 6z\"></path></svg></a>感想</h2>\n<p>我覺得這個很炫酷，我應該可以用在現有的前端開發項目，比如說博客，還有在做的一個在線學習編程平台上。如果你希望看到我如何應用 Titanic 的話，你可以打個星，關注一下我的博客。</p>","tableOfContents":"<ul>\n<li>\n<p><a href=\"/2017/07/06/titanic-a-set-of-animated-icons/#%E5%AE%89%E8%A3%9D%E6%96%B9%E6%B3%95\">安裝方法</a></p>\n<ul>\n<li><a href=\"/2017/07/06/titanic-a-set-of-animated-icons/#cdn\">CDN</a></li>\n<li><a href=\"/2017/07/06/titanic-a-set-of-animated-icons/#npm\">npm</a></li>\n<li><a href=\"/2017/07/06/titanic-a-set-of-animated-icons/#%E4%BD%BF%E7%94%A8%E4%BD%A0%E8%87%AA%E5%B7%B1%E7%9A%84%E5%82%99%E4%BB%BD\">使用你自己的備份</a></li>\n</ul>\n</li>\n<li><a href=\"/2017/07/06/titanic-a-set-of-animated-icons/#api\">API</a></li>\n<li><a href=\"/2017/07/06/titanic-a-set-of-animated-icons/#%E4%BE%8B%E5%AD%90\">例子</a></li>\n<li><a href=\"/2017/07/06/titanic-a-set-of-animated-icons/#%E5%8E%9F%E4%BD%9C%E8%80%85%E7%9A%84%E8%A9%B1\">原作者的話</a></li>\n<li><a href=\"/2017/07/06/titanic-a-set-of-animated-icons/#%E6%84%9F%E6%83%B3\">感想</a></li>\n</ul>","excerpt":"如果你用過 Font Awesome 等圖標，你可能會覺得它們很好看，用起來很很方便。但是，在用戶點擊這些圖標的時候，它們是不會有反應的。如果有這些圖標會動的話，那就更加好。Titanic 提供一系列的動畫圖標，以及以 JavaScript…","fields":{"slug":"/2017/07/06/titanic-a-set-of-animated-icons/"},"frontmatter":{"id":"2017-07-06a","title":"簡單易用的開源 JavaScript 動畫圖標庫 -- Titanic","slug":"/2017/07/06/titanic-a-set-of-animated-icons/","date":"2017-07-06T03:48:03.125Z","headerImage":null}},"previous":null,"next":null}]}},"pageContext":{"isCreatedByStatefulCreatePages":false,"id":"02efefb7-8227-5157-b159-c4fe029845c9","index":34}}